<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Sep1935"><font color="red">13 September 1935</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): Mr Joyce &hellip; is at present out of town and I am seeing him only once a week &hellip; by Tuesday morning (17 September 1935) as I am going down to him on that day in the afternoon. </div>
